v 0.2-1:
*) Release Date: 30-Nov-2010

*) Minor changes in documentation
*) R functions were split up into individual files

New Functions:
*) 'plotbandsonly': -) Adds uncertainty bounds to an existing plot

Modifications:
*) 'ggof'     : -) argument '...' is used now. 
                -) New argument: 'lab.fmt', for specifying the format of the axis' labels
*) 'plotbands': -) argument 'ylab' is used now. 
                -) argument 'cex.axis' is used now. 
                -) argument 'cex.lab' is used now. 
                -) argument 'legend' can now be logical (FALSE), in order to allow not having it.
                -) New argument 'ylim'
                -) New argument: 'lab.fmt', for specifying the format of the axis' labels
		-) 'sim' is now correctly plotted when 'type="points"' is used.
*) 'plot2'    : -) New argument: 'lab.fmt', for specifying the format of the axis' labels

